57.7	House_of_Leaves	House of Leaves	House of Leaves is the debut novel by the American author Mark Z. Danielewski, published by Pantheon Books. The novel quickly became a bestseller following its March 7, 2000 release. It was followed by a companion piece, The Whalestoe Letters. The novel has since been translated into a number of languages.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/de/House_of_leaves.jpg/200px-House_of_leaves.jpg
